  • No Driver & Bluetooth Setting Required: This HP active stylus pen doesn't need a Bluetooth connection. You just need to insert the battery and it will work immediately. Comes with 3 pen tips, replacing can be done within a second with the tool, extending the lifetime of the stylus.
  • 1024 Level Pressure point & High Sensitivity: 1024 level pressure point improves accuracy & precise for stylish pens, won't scratch the screen, no skips, no lagging, write more freely. Giving you a real creative feeling as on paper, suitable for drawing, browsing, playing games, and taking notes.
  • Low Power Consumption & Double Button Function: The supplied AAAA battery can be used normally for more than 400 days for normal use and 521-day standby, you dont need to carry a charging cable or worry about charging problems. The higher key is right-clicked function, the Lower key is the eraser function or dormancy aroused function.
